sources.title: Jerry Warren | The Incredible Petrified World (Sci-Fi, 1959) with John Carradine | Colorized
sources.description:
Dive into Danger: The ocean's deepest secret lies within. 
The crew of an oceanic expedition becomes stranded on the ocean floor in a mysterious cave system after their diving bell malfunctions. They must overcome challenges of survival, including encounters with an old cave dweller and a volcanic eruption, while a dramatic rescue operation is launched.

Original title: The Incredible Petrified World

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/4RkGHF118t0


This film is available with subtitles in many language options.

Director: Jerry Warren
Writer: John W. Steiner
Stars: John Carradine, Robert Clarke, Phyllis Coates 
Genres: Colorized classics, Action, Adventure, Sci-Fi, Thriller
